Har sur aur har bol dil ko itni khushi aur tasalli deta hai, ke lagta hai jaise rooh ko choo gaya ho. Is gaane ka classy andaaz aur traditional qawwali ka junoon, dono milkar isse ek masterpiece bana dete hain.
❤❤
